      "description": [
        "{{sbc|Innate:}} '''Udyr''' gains {{sti|ms|{{as|5 '''bonus''' movement speed}}}} and {{sti|{{as|10% '''bonus''' attack speed}}}} for 5 seconds every time he uses an ability, stacking up to 3 times, up to a maximum of {{sti|ms|{{as|15 '''bonus''' movement speed}}}} and {{sti|{{as|30% '''bonus''' attack speed}}}}.",
        "{{sbc|Four Stances:}} '''Udyr''' has no [[Champion ability|ultimate ability]] and instead has 4 [[Champion ability|basic abilities]]. Each of his abilities provides a passive effect that lasts until he activates a different ability, called his current ''Stance''. Activating any of his abilities will prevent his previous ''Stance'' from triggering any more on-hit effects, and will prevent him from activating another ability for 2 seconds.",
        "Starting at level 16, all abilities can gain a 6th rank."
      ],
      "notes": "* Instead of granting ultimate {{tip|cooldown reduction}}, {{bi|Cloudbringer's Grace}} from {{ui|Cloud Drake}} grants {{pp|4|key=%|type=stacks|5 to 5*4}} reduced global cooldown.\n* Further stance activations at maximum stacks of ''Monkey's Agility'' will refresh the timer.\n* Despite having 4 abilities each with 6 ranks, '''Udyr''' is not able to level beyond the usual limit under normal circumstances - meaning he must choose how to allocate his points and will not be able to reach maximum rank on each of his abilities, except in the featured game mode, {{tip|Ultra Rapid Fire}}.",
